These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: coffee, almond-milk, tea, soy-milk
Sport: volleyball, rugby, baseball, cricket
1. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Sport:baseball##1
2. Sport:cricket is on the far left##1
3. Sport:baseball is between Sport:rugby and Beverage:almond-milk##2
4. Beverage:soy-milk is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:tea is between Beverage:almond-milk and Beverage:coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk         | almond-milk   | tea | coffee       |
| Sport      | cricket | volleyball | baseball   | rugby |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: chess, sudoku, fishing, drawing
Nationality: indian, spanish, mexican, indonesian
1. Nationality:indonesian is between Hobby:fishing and Nationality:spanish##2
2. Hobby:drawing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:mexican is on the right of Nationality:indian##1
4. Hobby:chess is on the left of Nationality:indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | chess | fishing | drawing |
| Nationality   | spanish    | indonesian   | indian | mexican       |

